## Portfolio Usage Guidelines

**Q11: I want to put these projects in my portfolio. Is that allowed?**
**A:** Absolutely! Just make sure you actually built them yourself by following the course, and that you understand what you did. What is **not allowed** is creating your own course, videos, articles, or tutorials based on this course's content.

This license applies to the code and structure of the project. All visual assets (images, icons, fonts) used in this project are from the course materials and should not be reused in your own works without proper attribution or permission.

